# Fix Regression Guard

Read and follow the project skill: [.cursor/skills/fix-regression-guard/SKILL.md](.cursor/skills/fix-regression-guard/SKILL.md)

## Non-negotiable

> when ever a fix is done please make sure its corresponding test is enabled and so that next time if any fix is done those fixes are not lost

Before finishing any bug fix in this repo:

1. Add or update a regression test in the right `__tests__/` (or backend test) folder
2. Run `npm run test:ci` in `mobile_isolated/` when touching mobile code
3. Confirm Android CI runs tests before APK/AAB build (`.github/workflows/android-apk.yml`, `android-aab.yml`)
4. Bump versioned cache keys when stale on-device cache can hide the fix

Do not mark the task complete without passing tests and naming which test file guards the fix.
